	<name>4KWALL</name>
	<summary>Set 4K, HD and live wallpapers for your desktop background</summary>
	<description>
		<p>ABOUT 4KWALL :</p>
		<p>4kWall is a fast wallpaper manager and changer for Linux. Browse, download, and set stunning 4K, UHD, and HD wallpapers as your desktop background in a single click, with thousands of high-resolution images to choose from.</p>
		<p>FEATURES :</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Browse Millions of Wallpapers: Explore a huge collection of stunning HD, 4K and 8K wallpapers from the internet</li>
				<li>High-Quality Wallpaper Downloads: Download wallpapers in their original full resolution</li>
				<li>One-Click Wallpaper Setting: Apply any wallpaper to your desktop instantly</li>
				<li>Auto Wallpaper Changer: Automatically rotate your wallpaper at your preferred interval</li>
				<li>Different Wallpaper Per Monitor: Set a unique wallpaper on each connected monitor</li>
				<li>Smart Search and Color Filters: Find wallpapers by keyword, resolution, category, ratio and color</li>
				<li>Favourite Collections: Organize your favourite wallpapers into custom collections</li>
				<li>Supports HD, 4K and 8K Displays: Optimized for high-resolution and ultrawide monitors</li>
				<li>System Tray Integration: Change wallpapers quickly without leaving your workflow</li>
				<li>Clean, Modern Dark UI: A polished, distraction-free interface built for your desktop</li>
				<li>Regular Wallpaper Library Updates: Discover fresh wallpapers added regularly</li>
    		</ul>
		 <p>WHAT SETS 4KWALL APART ?</p>
			<ul>
			<li>Millions of high-quality HD, 4K and 8K wallpapers</li>
			<li>Powerful wallpaper search with color filtering</li>
			<li>Automatic wallpaper rotation</li>
			<li>Multi-monitor wallpaper support</li>
			<li>Auto rotation starts with login</li>
			<li>Regular updates with new wallpapers and features</li>
			</ul>
	</description>
